    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226820/extras/e80cf48d0a5cb11916efb1e1da4ac81f.avif?t=1673731546\" width=600 height=135 /></span><br>Agent J, you are chosen because of your mental capacities! Recurring transmissions will take to the Earth in 1 billion years. See breathtaking things and gain the knowledge for your research. You have to find out how life deals with the deadly power of the Sun.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226820/extras/9596465e3ecff4a339a220c0008910a0.poster.avif?t=1673731546\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226820/extras/9596465e3ecff4a339a220c0008910a0.webm?t=1673731546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226820/extras/9596465e3ecff4a339a220c0008910a0.mp4?t=1673731546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226820/extras/01bad65cd974d5c85a2b840ea0c3b83e.avif?t=1673731546\" width=600 height=135 /></span><br>Discuss the weird future lifeforms with your assistant, Agent C. Show what you have learned during the transmissions. Along the way, you carve out a unique relationship with her. Are you more the obedient type or a dissenter?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226820/extras/d39204af232b2d5f7f11c355ec373332.poster.avif?t=1673731546\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226820/extras/d39204af232b2d5f7f11c355ec373332.webm?t=1673731546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226820/extras/d39204af232b2d5f7f11c355ec373332.mp4?t=1673731546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226820/extras/f3ec4ca92d24bcb44f961a7fe8293cc5.avif?t=1673731546\" width=600 height=135 /></span><br>Agent C wants you to take a psyche test to evaluate your qualities as a researcher. You will obtain one of 3 character perks: humanizing, horrified or contaminated. It will be locked in mid-game and provide unique experiences in both the transmissions and the dialogues with Agent C.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226820/extras/fc3c48c6c7924c358453f64071a94a6b.poster.avif?t=1673731546\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226820/extras/fc3c48c6c7924c358453f64071a94a6b.webm?t=1673731546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226820/extras/fc3c48c6c7924c358453f64071a94a6b.mp4?t=1673731546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226820/extras/7e52526fda3e6e645e6f5373d7a1e7c9.avif?t=1673731546\" width=600 height=135 /></span><br>Learn about Arthur Klaassen, the discoverer of Eon of the Green. Agent C will share parts of his diary with you. But the circumstances of his death remain mysterious. Are you willing to reveal them?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226820/extras/2574c53600c7b7ae2b5b9e5d39b2b7d2.poster.avif?t=1673731546\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226820/extras/2574c53600c7b7ae2b5b9e5d39b2b7d2.webm?t=1673731546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226820/extras/2574c53600c7b7ae2b5b9e5d39b2b7d2.mp4?t=1673731546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>unique game loop of text-based interaction and visuals<br></li><li>120k + words of interactive fiction<br></li><li>dozens of experimental CGI cut scenes with sound, simulating mental time travel<br></li><li>recording player's choices and obtaining a character perk to provide even more unique experiences<br></li><li>several musical themes to enhance the game's atmosphere</li></ul>",
